data.eml:eml: Description of a new Psychoda Latreille species from Fennoscandia (Diptera: Psychodidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Salmela, Jukka, Kvifte, Gunnar M., More, Anna (2012): Description of a new Psychoda Latreille species from Fennoscandia (Diptera: Psychodidae). Zootaxa 3313: 34-43, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.281070
